snippet.title: Ghostbusters: Spirits Unleashed Map Showcase: New Motion Club
snippet.description:
The New Motion Club is a pillar of the New York underground music scene. After a change in ownership, there has been a recent spike in paranormal activity.

Ghostbusters: Spirits Unleashed is available on PC on EPIC GAMES, PS4™, PS4™Pro, PS5™, Xbox Series X|S and Xbox One. To learn more about the game visit: https://www.ghostbusterssu.com/
